                    <div class="founder-qualifications">
                        <h4>Qualifications & Achievements</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>PhD in Political Science from University of Delhi</li>
                            <li>15+ Years of Teaching Experience</li>
                            <li>Author of 3 Best-selling UGC NET Preparation Books</li>
                            <li>Regular Contributor to Education Magazines</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
